org.paces.Stata.Google

Class Geocode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.paces.Stata.Google.Geocode

  • public class Geocode
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to geocode the addresses requested by the user. The class includes methods used to format the address string, call the Google Geocode API, parse the payload, and return the results to the user.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    Billy Buchanan
